<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.5.7">
<l>ēṉō rañca veñcamattu ḷariyāyp pariya viraṇiyaṉai</l>
<l>ūṉā rakalam piḷaveṭutta voruvaṉ tāṉē yirucuṭarāy</l>
<l>vāṉāyt tīyāy mārutamāy malaiyā yalainī rulakaṉaittum</l>
<l>tāṉāy tāṉu māṉāṉtaṉ cāḷak kirāma maṭaineñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Heart, take refuge in Śālagrāma of the very unique one who, in heated battle</l>
<l>When [he] as a lion, lifted massive Hiraṇya to split his flesh-full chest</l>
<l rend="indent">so the others were frightened,</l>
<l>The one who also became the two luminaries, the sky, fire, wind, mountains,</l>
<l>The earth with crashing waves – everything and himself.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
